Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:42.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Myoga...\NI hope you're not deceiving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:46.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Has this Inu-whatever\nreally mastered the Tetsusaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:48.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His name is Master Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha? Oh, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The son of the Dog General...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:55.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who gave me his fang\nfrom which to forge the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:58.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he the younger\nof the two doltish brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:00.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It happened only once...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:06.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but with one swing,\nhe killed a hundred demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:09.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being accused of abandoning you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:10.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}isn't something I'll enjoy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}waking up to in the morning!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:26.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But there's been nothing ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:28.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I'm stumped as to what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:31.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then...\nmaybe I should just test him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:37.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to see whether he's deserving of the\nfamous Tetsusaiga which I forged.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:02.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-hot! H-hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a place this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even the rocky ground is burning hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mmm... the smell of roasting meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:12.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you here, Totosai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope you have completed\nthe sword that was commissioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the promised date of delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:38.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:40.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Moved"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:47.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn that sneaky badger!\NWhere'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:54.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see... So Totosai has run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please forgive me,\NMaster Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:04:00.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The swordsmith Totosai\nis a man of extreme likes and dislikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From what I have heard,\nhe will create a sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,only if he takes a liking to the client.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:08.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words,\nhe has no intention of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:11.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,making a sword that suits me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:16.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... How can I put it...\NHe doesn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:20.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-you're smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please get angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:28.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I fear a smiling\NMaster Sesshomaru much, much more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:37.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My life was shortened\nby a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My Sacred Jewel fragments\nwere taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:58.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That wasn't all there\nis of the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll just start collecting 'em\none by one again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:09.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's so unlike Inuyasha.\NWhy's he being so understanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:13.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, because the one who stole\nthe Sacred Jewel fragments was Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:16.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez... A crime committed by\nthe woman he loves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:22.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you implying that\NI'm trying to defend Kikyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?! Do you think that, too...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you have any complaints,\njust speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:36.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:39.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Up above?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:49.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am called Totosai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Draw your sword, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:59.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The old geezer...knows me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:02.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you refuse,\NI'll go on the offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get back, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He thwarted the Tetsusaiga\nwith his hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The resonance is way too dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:25.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe this kid isn't the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:35.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He stopped the sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With a piece of leather!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:40.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The blade is full of chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been too rough with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,J-just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai, isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The swordsmith\nwho forged the Tetsusaiga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:01.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I, Totosai, forged the Tetsusaiga\nfrom a fang your father gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the world of\nsword-wielding demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am famous\namong those who know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:09.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and among those who don't know,\NI'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Doesn't it mean that\nhe's not very famous at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:15.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what does the swordsmith\nwant with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I took a good look at\nthe Tetsusaiga earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:26.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was the sword of swords,\nforged by a master swordsmith...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:29.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but the sound of the steel\nis terribly dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:31.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a very sad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:34.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're picking a fight,\njust say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:35.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga, the Tetsusaiga can't be\nused by someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:44.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so short-tempered and\nso eager to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:47.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So rather than blindly relying\non the Tetsusaiga's strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:50.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and fighting recklessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:53.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,better for Inuyasha to just\ngive up the sword, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:56.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, the sooner the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll just break the Tetsusaiga\nin two now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:02.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What didja say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:06.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You may have made the sword,\nbut now, it belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:10.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I won't break it.\NSorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:13.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop hedging.\NWhat are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At night, when everyone has\nsettled down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will quietly steal it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, no... I won't steal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:20.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,as it is, you won't be able to master\nthe mystery of the Tetsusaiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:28.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which enables one to slay a\nhundred demons in one sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:32.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this Totosai knows\nits secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:34.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think you both need to\nget to know each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:38.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and you must cooperate to awaken\nthe Tetsusaiga's true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What mystery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get the hang of it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:46.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are collecting fragments\nof the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:50.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Some time has passed since the\nfragments were scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:54.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There may even be a\ndemon who already possesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,two or three fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to destroy a demon whose\nstrength is enhanced...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:02.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,don't you want the Tetsusaiga to be\nawakened to its true potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, he has a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:07.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think you should listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what'm I supposed to do, Totosai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:16.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone seeks my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:17.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:21.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is a fool who has ordered\nme to forge a sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:24.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to rival the power of the Tetsusaiga...\nelse he will kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:28.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Show me that you can\nprotect me from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you say "please"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:35.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I never heard of that!\NDescribe this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:40.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He has white hair and wears\nfurry, warm-Iooking clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Another old geezer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:44.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:48.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait a minute... If he's dressed\nlike that... and not old... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he wants a sword stronger\nthan the Tetsusaiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:51.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could he be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:55.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:00.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:08.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So he {\i1}is{\i0} the one who's after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:14.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Exactly! It's that Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:19.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... why do you\nplot with Totosai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:23.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? To punish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:27.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Totosai... I see you\nare rushing headlong into death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no... I just thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:33.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,after you beat Inuyasha, maybe\NI can make you a new sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Just a thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! What you said earlier\nis the exact opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:40.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:45.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai, do not forget\nwhat you just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You heard him, Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:52.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can die for the sake\nof my new sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, hurry and get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:55.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill you instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They are both so hot-headed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the one who instigated this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:15.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:16.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:20.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No wonder he's Old Myoga's friend!\NActing so innocent!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Old Myoga...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you, Myoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome,\NOld Myoga is on Miroku's shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:31.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry here!\NIt's dangerous over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:32.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:54.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gotta be kidding!\NNo good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:07.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Myoga...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:11.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,has Inuyasha really mastered\nthe Tetsusaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:19.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, each time it's Inuyasha\nwho ends up beating Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miss, are you sure you\nhaven't been dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:33.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai... do you not\nfeel sad for the Tetsusaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The famous sword is no\nbetter than a piece of log.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:39.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All Inuyasha does is\nswing it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:43.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Depending on its user,\na sword can live or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A wise observation...\nmy opinion precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! You can cut your jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm only warming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:59.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be shocked at my real power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:00.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no... the blood's rushed\nto his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:17.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Totosai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,do you still refuse\nto make me a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:31.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing, stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:37.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you absolutely refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:45.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have already made you\na fine sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That famous sword at your hip:\NTenseiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:53.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I, Totosai, made the sword from\na fang given to me by your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Tenseiga for the older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Tetsusaiga for the younger one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:01.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that was your father's last will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is a great sword of swords...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:06.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,no worse and no better\nthan the Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:09.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you learn to love it more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:13.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that old man also made\NSesshomaru's sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:16.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, in all the battles until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:19.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never seen Sesshomaru\nunsheathe that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:20.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:24.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You dare imply that this stupid,\nuseless sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:26.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is worthy of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:30.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! He's angry! He's angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:34.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess I'll take my leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They've escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:05.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! You're so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:09.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why bother to have Inuyasha\nto protect you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when he's weaker than Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:14.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could Sesshomaru call his\ngreat sword useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:23.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,how could Inuyasha be so weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,how utterly wrong I was\nabout them both!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:26.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Owee!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am not weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:35.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old one... I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That sword Sesshomaru has...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it also a powerful sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, the Tenseiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:44.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You could say\nits power is awesome indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:47.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But when the Dog General\ncommissioned me to make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:51.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I questioned at first about\nits powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A sword that won't cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:56.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How're you supposed to fight\nwith a sword like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:16:00.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Tenseiga is not a sword\nyou use against foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:02.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To put it simply,\nit is a sword of healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:03.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Healing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:07.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,While the Tetsusaiga is the sword\nto defeat the powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:11.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Tenseiga is the sword to\nsave the lives of the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:13.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Save lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:17.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If one has the true kindness\nof heart towards people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:20.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Tenseiga has the power to\nsave a hundred people in one sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:22.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kindness of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Tetsusaiga can kill\na hundred in one sweep...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:30.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,while the Tenseiga can save\na hundred in one sweep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:33.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And does this sword\nfunction as a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is able to bring back dead souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:39.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In this Feudal era,\nit can be used in many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:44.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I intended to name the sword,\N"Coffin-Cheater"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:47.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but it was christened with\na fancy name like Tenseiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:50.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it was your father\nthat named it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:55.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No wonder Sesshomaru\nwants a new sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A sword to help others...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,no way that guy'd have any use for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:05.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't it work out?\NIt was your father's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Given your brother's personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:10.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wouldn't be happy with it,\neven if he could use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A very nice roast, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:23.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't eat it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! My meat's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You just ate it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:29.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Who are you anyway?\NAnd where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was not aware of it, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that the sword is also\nyour father's memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:53.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What kind of power does it have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:57.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want to know, Jaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:01.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It makes me extremely curious\nabout the two swords...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,forged from your father's fang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:07.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The two swords are like... brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:12.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no... I didn't mean to compare\nthem with you and Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:15.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not concerned at all that you\nwho hate half-demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,would be related to Inuyasha...\nwell, I am concerned, but!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:19.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:21.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:46.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:47.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:49.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:53.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:54.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was slain just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:18:59.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you see now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:03.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This Tenseiga is a sword\nthat cannot kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:06.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:09.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:16.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:23.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did my father bestow\nthis Tenseiga upon{\i0} me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:26.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the Tetsusaiga upon Inuyasha?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have a gift now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:57.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us go and see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:00.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:13.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:15.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:18.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See you? You plan to escape alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't rely on Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:22.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:26.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who needs an old geezer like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:31.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You cannot use the Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:35.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will break it into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup, you geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:40.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's frank, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:51.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't tell whether that\nold man is strong or weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:55.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Poor thing... That Inuyasha\nwill be killed by Sesshomaru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, Inuyasha hasn't\neven been able to see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:01.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the "Wind Scar" which\nawakens the Tetsusaiga's power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:05.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you going after him,\NInuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:08.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were lucky enough to\nmeet the Tetsusaiga's maker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! That old fool is full of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:29.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:31.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:34.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will tear both you\nand Inuyasha into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:37.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:38.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:42.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old one... you don't want to make\NSesshomaru a new sword, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:43.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:50.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've had it up to here with\nall this about Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:53.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's about time\nto settle this once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:57.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:01.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It will all end today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:04.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as you cannot see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:06.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the "Wind Scar."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.96,0:23:52.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's father had given\nhis two sons each a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.79,0:23:54.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the older brother Sesshomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:57.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,doesn't like that\NInuyasha has the Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The mystery of the "Wind Scar"\nis finally revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.57,0:24:02.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha totally defeats Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.44,0:24:05.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sword of life,\nthe Tenseiga, is drawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.67,0:24:08.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whose life does Sesshomaru\nends up saving?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.31,0:24:12.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The True Owner of the Great Sword!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.91,0:24:14.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
